Products.Name: Continental Pasta Bacon & Parmesan Boscaiola
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Continental Pasta Bacon & Parmesan Boscaiola' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL PASTA & SAUCE BACON & PARMESAN 96 GR

It’s time to welcome Continental to your midweek cooking repertoire. We have a range of delicious gourmet pasta, rice and risotto flavours to help you create an easy and delicious meal any night of the week. This Boscaiola with Bacon & Parmesan Pasta is made with responsibly grown Australian wheat and contains real bacon, mushroom and parmesan cheese, combined into a creamy and earthy Italian classic. Create your own twist by stirring through some cooked chicken and peas. Before serving sprinkle with chopped parsley and shaved parmesan. All of our Continental Gourmet Pastas contain no artificial colours, flavours or added MSG. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. How we preserve and lock in flavour in our products is just as important as how we grow our vegetables in the first place. That can mean drying, freezing, boiling, or turning them into paste – whatever suits the Continental recipe they’ll be making. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.

No artificial colours

No artificial flavours

No added MSG

Serves 3

Made with responsibly grown Australian wheat

Made with real pasta, spinach, parmesan cheese and bacon

Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL RISOTTO PUMPKIN BACON & SOUR CREAM 115 GR

It’s time to welcome Continental to your midweek cooking repertoire. We have a range of delicious gourmet pasta, rice and risotto flavours to help you create an easy and delicious meal any night of the week. Made with responsibly grown New Zealand pumpkins, this Pumpkin, Bacon & Sour Cream Risotto is sure to be a ‘go-to’ during cold winter nights. Stir through goat’s cheese and baby spinach and sprinkle with toasted pine nuts for a hearty, satisfying dinner. All of our Continental Gourmet Risottos contain no artificial colours, flavours or added MSG. This Pumpkin, Bacon & Sour Cream Risotto is made with real rice, pumpkin, bacon and sour cream. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. How we preserve and lock in flavour in our products is just as important as how we grow our vegetables in the first place. That can mean drying, freezing, boiling, or turning them into paste – whatever suits the Continental recipe they’ll be making. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.

Products.Name: Continental Rice Spinach Ricotta Parmesan
Products.SupplyLimitMessage: 'Continental Rice Spinach Ricotta Parmesan' has a supply limit of 36. The quantity in your cart has been reduced accordingly. To purchase a larger quantity, please contact us on 1800 000 610. Please note we do not supply trade orders.
Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL RICE SPINACH RICOTTA PARMESAN 105 GR

This Spinach Ricotta & Parmesan Rice & Quinoa brings together a perfectly matched flavour combination for a wholesome dish. For a more complete meal, why not add some chicken and steamed veggies, and top with a little extra Parmesan to finish it off! At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. How we preserve and lock in flavour in our products is just as important as how we grow our vegetables in the first place. That can mean drying, freezing, boiling, or turning them into paste – whatever suits the Continental recipe they’ll be making. Drying is one of the oldest ways to preserve food there is, going back thousands of years. It’s simple, safe and helps keep the colour, aroma and flavour of our ingredients for longer - naturally. We don’t need to add any preservatives, and it protects the natural flavour. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.

No artificial colours

No artificial flavours

No added MSG

Prepared in under 10 minutes

Serves 3

Made with responsibly grown spinach

Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL RICE TERIYAKI & GARLIC 115 GR

Continental has a range of delicious gourmet pasta, rice and risotto flavours to help you create an easy and delicious meal any night of the week. This delicious Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice evokes the very best of Japanese cuisine. Rich in authentic teriyaki flavour with a kick of garlic, every mouthful is bursting with gourmet flavours. For a little something extra stir through some sliced char-grilled beef fillet and green beans and top with spring onion and toasted sesame seeds. All of our Continental Gourmet Side Dish Rices contain no artificial colours, flavours or added MSG. Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice is made with real rice, soy sauce, garlic. At Continental, we love food the way you do. We know how much you value good, nutritious, flavourful food, as well as authentic home cooking. It feels good to cook, and even better to bring pleasure to the ones you love, through the food you put on the table. How we preserve and lock in flavour in our products is just as important as how we grow our vegetables in the first place. That can mean drying, freezing, boiling, or turning them into paste – whatever suits the Continental recipe they’ll be making. For over 50 years now, our chefs at Continental have combined their expertise, love of flavour, and only the finest ingredients to help you create great tasting meals every day.

Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice has no artificial colours.

Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice has no artificial flavours.

Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice has no added MSG.

Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice is made with Real Rice, Soy Sauce and Garlic.

Continental Gourmet Teriyaki & Garlic Rice is seasoned, fluffy rice every time.

Products.RichDescription:
CONTINENTAL RISOTTO ROAST CHICKEN & LEEK 115 GR

It’s time to welcome Continental to your midweek cooking repertoire. We have a range of delicious gourmet pasta, rice and risotto flavours to help you create an easy and delicious meal any night of the week. This Roast Chicken & Leek Risotto is a gourmet twist on a home-style roast chicken classic that will make every day feel like a Sunday. CONTINENTAL PASTA CHICKEN PESTO & SPRING ONION 92 GR

It’s time to welcome Continental to your midweek cooking repertoire. We have a range of delicious gourmet pasta, rice and risotto flavours to help you create an easy and delicious meal any night of the week. This Chicken, Pesto & Spring Onion Pasta uses our perfectly crafted Orecchiette pasta to capture every drop of flavour for a tantalising dish. Why not stir through some sliced char-grilled chicken and asparagus and top with toasted pine nuts and basil. All of our Continental Gourmet Pastas contain no artificial colours, flavours or added MSG. This Chicken, Pesto & Spring Onion Pasta is made with responsibly grown Australian wheat and contains real pasta, chicken, parmesan cheese, basil, garlic and spring onion.
